==註腳==
專輯內的小冊子上，某些歌曲的歌詞加上了一些註腳。
* "[[Spiders_(歌曲)|Spiders]]" :
<blockquote>''"Your thoughts, and dreams are no longer sacred, as they are exposed to a<br/>weapon known as {{Link-en|remote viewing|remote viewing|remote viewing}} and monitoring."''</blockquote>
<blockquote>(原文翻釋：你的思想、夢想不再神聖，因為他們被暴露於名為「{{Link-en|遠程觀察|remote viewing|遠程觀察}}」和「監視」的武器裡。)</blockquote>

* "DDevil" :
<blockquote>''"For those that control the [[central_nervous_system|central nervous system]],<br/>control society, and the world.''"</blockquote>
<blockquote>(原文翻釋：給予那些控制[[中樞神經系統|中樞神經系統]]、控制社會以及世界的人。)</blockquote>

* "War?" :
<blockquote>''"We first fought the heathens in the name of religion, then {{Link-en|Communism|Communism|Communism}}, and now in<br/>the name of drugs and terrorism. Our excuses for global domination always change."''</blockquote>
<blockquote>(原文翻釋：我們首先以宗教的名義，然後再以[[共產主義|共產主義]]、以毒品和恐怖主義的名義與異教徒鬥爭，我們在全球統治的藉口上總是一直在改變。)</blockquote>

* "Mind" :
<blockquote>''"{{Link-en|Mind control|Mind control|Mind control}} technology has been used by the [[Central_Intelligence_Agency|CIA]] since the 1950s as part of<br/>their non-lethal, covert weapons program."''</blockquote>
<blockquote>(原文翻釋：自20世紀50年代以來，[[中央情報局|中央情報局]]一直使用[[心靈控制|心靈控制]]的技術作為其非致命的隱蔽武器計劃的一部分。)</blockquote>

* "Peephole" :
<blockquote>''"The February 18 edition of Britain's [[New_Scientist|NEW SCIENTIST]] Magazine reports that the<br/>Geneva-based [[World_Health_Organization|World Health Organization]] suppressed, under political pressure,<br/>a report which confirmed that marijuana is safer than either alcohol or tobacco."''</blockquote>
<blockquote>(原文翻釋：英國的《[[新科學人|新科學人]]雜誌》於2月18號的出版中稱，總部位於日內瓦的[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]在政治壓力下壓制了一份報告，證實大麻比酒精或煙草更安全。)</blockquote>

* "Darts" :
<blockquote>''"Why do old societies hold the pantheon of 12 gods to be true,<br/>while modern societies generally have one God?"''</blockquote>
<blockquote>(原文翻釋：為什麼舊有社會對於有[[奧林帕斯十二神|十二位神的萬神殿]]宗教予以意同，卻到現代社會通常只擁有一位神？)</blockquote>

* "P.L.U.C.K." :
<blockquote>''"System of a Down would like to dedicate this song to the memory of the 1.5<br/>million victims of the {{Link-en|Armenian Genocide|Armenian Genocide|Armenian Genocide}}, perpetrated by the Turkish<br/>Government in 1915."''</blockquote>
<blockquote>(原文翻釋：System Of A Down想把這首歌獻給於1915年土耳其政府對[[亞美尼亞人|亞美尼亞人]]所進行的[[亞美尼亞種族滅絕|亞美尼亞種族滅絕]]，當中屠殺的150萬受害者。)</blockquote>

